com.konakartadmin.app

Class AdminDataDescriptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.konakartadmin.app.AdminDataDescriptor

  • public class AdminDataDescriptor
extends java.lang.Object
    The AdminDataDescriptor is used in some methods where an array of objects is returned. It allows you to :
    • Apply a limit to the number of objects returned
    • Apply an offset, normally used for paging
    • Apply order by criteria
    • Return invisible objects by setting showInvisible to true
    • Apply criteria on the custom attributes. If a custom attribute is set, then only products with a matching custom attribute value are returned.
